POST http://localhost:8080/api/graphql HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

query {
  __schema {
    types {
      name
    }
  }
}

### Get job schema

POST http://localhost:8080/api/graphql HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

query {
  __type(name: "Job") {
    name
    fields {
      name
      type {
        kind
      }
      description
    }
  }
}

