### Get Jobs

POST http://localhost:8080/api/graphql HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

query {
    jobs {
        name
        args {
            name
            value
        }
        duration
        entrypoint
        tasks {
            script
            scriptFile
            onSuccess
            onFailure
        }
        status
    }
}

